      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "html": "<section id=\"shopify-section-template--24940377080074__before_after_image_qQ78FT\" class=\"shopify-section shopify-section--before-after-image\" style=\"--clip-path-offset: -145.6px;\"><style>\n  #shopify-section-template--24940377080074__before_after_image_qQ78FT {\n    --section-background-hash: 0;\n  }\n\n  #shopify-section-template--24940377080074__before_after_image_qQ78FT + * {\n    --previous-section-background-hash: 0;\n  }</style>\n<style>\n  #shopify-section-template--24940377080074__before_after_image_qQ78FT {\n    --section-stack-intro: 33.3333%;\n    --section-stack-main: 66.6667%;\n\n    --before-after-initial-drag-position: 63%;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"section   section-blends section-full\">\n  <div class=\"section-stack section-stack--horizontal \">\n<div class=\"section-stack__intro\">\n        <div class=\"prose \">\n          <p class=\"subheading\">TESTÉ CLINIQUEMENT</p>\n<h2 class=\"h2\">Nous ne promettons pas des résultats. Nous les prouvons.</h2>\n<p>Des études cliniques indépendantes, ainsi que des milliers de clientes satisfaites, confirment l’efficacité de notre <strong>Masque au Bio-Collagène</strong>.<br><br>Dès les premières applications, la peau paraît <strong>plus ferme, plus lisse et plus éclatante</strong>, avec une <strong>réduction visible des ridules, des taches pigmentaires et des cernes</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Voyez la différence dès la 1ère utilisation.</strong></p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n<div class=\"section-stack__main\">\n      <div class=\"before-after shadow  text-custom\" style=\"--text-color: 255 255 255;\">\n        <div class=\"before-after__before-image  text-custom\" style=\"--text-color: 255 255 255;\">\n<picture><img src=\"//leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/Untitled_design_35_430x_1.webp?v=1758389676&amp;width=430\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"//leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/Untitled_design_35_430x_1.webp?v=1758389676&amp;width=300 300w, //leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/Untitled_design_35_430x_1.webp?v=1758389676&amp;width=400 400w\" width=\"430\" height=\"430\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 999px) 100vw, 1000px\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"rounded w-full\"></picture><p class=\"before-after__label before-after__label--left before-after__label--top h5\">Before</p>\n</div>\n\n        <div class=\"before-after__after-image  text-custom\" style=\"--text-color: 255 255 255;\">\n<picture><img src=\"//leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/6_e6c68bde-2a27-48a5-bbf6-b8e3729c07ff_430x_1.webp?v=1758389684&amp;width=430\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"//leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/6_e6c68bde-2a27-48a5-bbf6-b8e3729c07ff_430x_1.webp?v=1758389684&amp;width=300 300w, //leaf-cosmetics.com/cdn/shop/files/6_e6c68bde-2a27-48a5-bbf6-b8e3729c07ff_430x_1.webp?v=1758389684&amp;width=400 400w\" width=\"430\" height=\"430\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 999px) 100vw, 1000px\" class=\"object-fill rounded\" draggable=\"false\"></picture><p class=\"before-after__label before-after__label--right before-after__label--top h5\">After</p>\n</div>\n\n        <div class=\"before-after__cursor-wrapper\">\n          <split-cursor class=\"before-after__cursor\" style=\"--background: 255 255 255\">\n            <span class=\"sr-only\">Tirer</span>\n\n            <svg role=\"presentation\" focusable=\"false\" width=\"28\" height=\"35\" viewbox=\"0 0 32 40\">\n              <path d=\"M0 16C0 7.16344 7.16344 0 16 0C24.8366 0 32 7.16344 32 16V24C32 32.8366 24.8366 40 16 40C7.16344 40 0 32.8366 0 24V16Z\" fill=\"#ffffff\"></path>\n              <path fill=\"#000000\" d=\"M11 14H13V26H11zM15 14H17V26H15zM19 14H21V26H19z\"></path>\n            </svg>\n          </split-cursor>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n</section>",
