        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "html": "<div id=\"shopify-section-template--24940377080074__before_after_reviews_xF9bed\" class=\"shopify-section\">\n\n<section id=\"before-after-reviews-template--24940377080074__before_after_reviews_xF9bed\" class=\"before-after-reviews-section\">\n  <!-- Titre de la section -->\n  <div class=\"reviews-heading-wrapper\">\n    <h2 class=\"reviews-heading\">\n      Voyez les Résultats par vous même\n    </h2>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"reviews-slider-container\">\n    <!-- Piste de slides -->\n    <div class=\"reviews-slider-track\" id=\"reviews-slider-track-template--24940377080074__before_after_reviews_xF9bed\" style=\"transform: translateX(0px);\">\n      \n        <div class=\"reviews-slide\">\n          <!-- Carte -->\n          <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <!-- Images avant/après -->\n            <div class=\"review-card__images\">\n              <div class=\"review-card__image-left\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/1_57ee3365-ccb2-437a-a54a-193f78b5671e.png?v=1763217814?crop=center&amp;height=500&amp;v=1740139298&amp;width=400\" alt=\"Before\" class=\"\" data-media-download-modified=\"true\" data-original-position=\"static\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n                \n                  <div class=\"review-badge-left\">AVANT</div>\n                \n              </div>\n              <div class=\"review-card__image-right\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/2_42173ccd-5104-47a6-a554-0442d3f5ed2d.png?v=1763217815?crop=center&amp;height=500&amp;v=1740139298&amp;width=400\" alt=\"After\" class=\"\" data-media-download-modified=\"true\" data-original-position=\"static\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n                \n                  <div class=\"review-badge-right\">APRÈS 6 SEMAINES</div>\n                \n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Contenu de l'avis -->\n            <div class=\"review-card__content\">\n              <!-- Nom, drapeau -->\n              <div class=\"review-user-info\">\n                \n                <span class=\"review-user-name\">Sophie, 52 ans</span>\n              </div>\n\n              <!-- Note + Titre -->\n              <div class=\"review-rating-title\">\n                <div class=\"review-stars\">\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n                      <path d=\"M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .67.418l1.898 3.845 4.243.617a.75.75 0 0 1 .415 1.279l-3.072 2.995.725 4.224a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.788 1.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.725-4.225-3.072-2.995A.75.75 0 0 1 1.19 4.73l4.243-.617L7.33.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n                      <path d=\"M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .67.418l1.898 3.845 4.243.617a.75.75 0 0 1 .415 1.279l-3.072 2.995.725 4.224a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.788 1.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.725-4.225-3.072-2.995A.75.75 0 0 1 1.19 4.73l4.243-.617L7.33.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n                      <path d=\"M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .67.418l1.898 3.845 4.243.617a.75.75 0 0 1 .415 1.279l-3.072 2.995.725 4.224a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.788 1.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.725-4.225-3.072-2.995A.75.75 0 0 1 1.19 4.73l4.243-.617L7.33.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n                      <path d=\"M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .67.418l1.898 3.845 4.243.617a.75.75 0 0 1 .415 1.279l-3.072 2.995.725 4.224a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.788 1.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.725-4.225-3.072-2.995A.75.75 0 0 1 1.19 4.73l4.243-.617L7.33.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n                      <path d=\"M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .67.418l1.898 3.845 4.243.617a.75.75 0 0 1 .415 1.279l-3.072 2.995.725 4.224a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.788 1.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.725-4.225-3.072-2.995A.75.75 0 0 1 1.19 4.73l4.243-.617L7.33.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                </div>\n                <strong class=\"review-title\">Une peau plus lisse et raffermie</strong>\n              </div>\n\n              <!-- Badge vérifié (image) -->\n              \n                <div class=\"review-verified\">\n                  <img class=\"review-verified-badge\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0828/6457/0634/files/badge-facebook.png?v=1739294501\" alt=\"Verified badge\">\n                  <span>Client vérifié</span>\n                </div>\n              \n\n              <!-- Texte -->\n              <div class=\"review-text\">\n                \"J’ai testé de nombreuses crèmes anti-âge, mais ce masque est le seul qui a vraiment fait la différence. Après quelques applications, mes rides sont moins marquées et ma peau est plus ferme. J’aurais aimé le découvrir plus tôt !\"\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      \n        <div class=\"reviews-slide\">\n          <!-- Carte -->\n          <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <!-- Images avant/après -->\n            <div class=\"review-card__images\">\n              <div class=\"review-card__image-left\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/3_9ccf463b-f4f7-40b5-95bc-be0febec1637.png?v=1763217815?crop=center&amp;height=500&amp;v=1740139091&amp;width=400\" alt=\"Before\" class=\"\" data-media-download-modified=\"true\" data-original-position=\"static\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n                \n                  <div class=\"review-badge-left\">AVANT</div>\n                \n              </div>\n              <div class=\"review-card__image-right\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/4_57b32c2e-d984-4d60-9fc0-4050dbc89a76.png?v=1763217814?crop=center&amp;height=500&amp;v=1740139091&amp;width=400\" alt=\"After\" class=\"\" data-media-download-modified=\"true\" data-original-position=\"static\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n                \n                  <div class=\"review-badge-right\">APRÈS 3 SEMAINES</div>\n                \n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Contenu de l'avis -->\n            <div class=\"review-card__content\">\n              <!-- Nom, drapeau -->\n              <div class=\"review-user-info\">\n                \n                <span class=\"review-user-name\">Nathalie, 47 ans</span>\n              </div>\n\n              <!-- Note + Titre -->\n              <div class=\"review-rating-title\">\n                <div class=\"review-stars\">\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n                      <path d=\"M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .67.418l1.898 3.845 4.243.617a.75.75 0 0 1 .415 1.279l-3.072 2.995.725 4.224a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.788 1.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.725-4.225-3.072-2.995A.75.75 0 0 1 1.19 4.73l4.243-.617L7.33.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n                      <path d=\"M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .67.418l1.898 3.845 4.243.617a.75.75 0 0 1 .415 1.279l-3.072 2.995.725 4.224a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.788 1.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.725-4.225-3.072-2.995A.75.75 0 0 1 1.19 4.73l4.243-.617L7.33.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n                      <path d=\"M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .67.418l1.898 3.845 4.243.617a.75.75 0 0 1 .415 1.279l-3.072 2.995.725 4.224a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.788 1.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.725-4.225-3.072-2.995A.75.75 0 0 1 1.19 4.73l4.243-.617L7.33.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n                      <path d=\"M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .67.418l1.898 3.845 4.243.617a.75.75 0 0 1 .415 1.279l-3.072 2.995.725 4.224a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.788 1.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.725-4.225-3.072-2.995A.75.75 0 0 1 1.19 4.73l4.243-.617L7.33.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n                      <path d=\"M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .67.418l1.898 3.845 4.243.617a.75.75 0 0 1 .415 1.279l-3.072 2.995.725 4.224a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.788 1.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.725-4.225-3.072-2.995A.75.75 0 0 1 1.19 4.73l4.243-.617L7.33.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                  \n                </div>\n                <strong class=\"review-title\">Un effet liftant immédiat</strong>\n              </div>\n\n              <!-- Badge vérifié (image) -->\n              \n                <div class=\"review-verified\">\n                  <img class=\"review-verified-badge\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0828/6457/0634/files/badge-facebook.png?v=1739294501\" alt=\"Verified badge\">\n                  <span>Client vérifié</span>\n                </div>\n              \n\n              <!-- Texte -->\n              <div class=\"review-text\">\n                \"Dès la première utilisation, j’ai ressenti un effet tenseur incroyable. Ma peau est plus souple et mes ridules autour des yeux sont visiblement atténuées. Je recommande à toutes celles qui veulent un soin efficace sans passer par des injections !\"\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      \n        <div class=\"reviews-slide\">\n          <!-- Carte -->\n          <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <!-- Images avant/après -->\n            <div class=\"review-card__images\">\n              <div class=\"review-card__image-left\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/5_5e2edf83-c640-4cee-aeda-9f21a0d5bfd9.png?v=1763217814?crop=center&amp;height=500&amp;v=1740139092&amp;width=400\" alt=\"Before\" class=\"\" data-media-download-modified=\"true\" data-original-position=\"static\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n                \n                  <div class=\"review-badge-left\">AVANT</div>\n                \n              </div>\n              <div class=\"review-card__image-right\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/6_0e1669e9-ca62-4ca9-86a2-683798e025c0.png?v=1763217814?crop=center&amp;height=500&amp;v=1740139091&amp;width=400\" alt=\"After\" class=\"\" data-media-download-modified=\"true\" data-original-position=\"static\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n                \n                  <div class=\"review-badge-right\">APRÈS 1 SEMAINE</div>\n                \n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Contenu de l'avis -->\n            <div class=\"review-card__content\">\n              <!-- Nom, drapeau -->\n              <div class=\"review-user-info\">\n                \n                <span class=\"review-user-name\">Léa, 28 ans</span>\n              </div>\n\n              <!-- Note + Titre -->\n              <div class=\"review-rating-title\">\n                <div class=\"review-stars\">\n                  \n                    <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#028763\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\