/Design_sans_titre_4.png?v=1763286680&amp;width=1000 1000w\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"min(100vw, var(--page-width))\" style=\"\"></div></div>\n      </div>\n<div class=\"rich-text justify-start md:hidden\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text__wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"prose justify-items-start text-start\">\n<p class=\"h2 hyphenate\">Pourquoi choisir le masque Leaf Cosmetics et pas un autre ?</p>\n<div><p>Pourquoi payer plus cher pour des résultats moins visibles ? Avec le Masque Leaf Cosmetics, profitez d’un soin premium à domicile, efficace dès la première application.</p></div>\n<div style=\"margin-block-start: 0px; position: relative;\" data-media-download-modified=\"true\" data-original-position=\"static\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/Design_sans_titre_4.png?v=1763286680?v=1728926100&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/Design_sans_titre_4.png?v=1763286680&amp;width=200 200w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/Design_sans_titre_4.png?v=1763286680&amp;width=300 300w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/Design_sans_titre_4.png?v=1763286680&amp;width=400 400w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/Design_sans_titre_4.png?v=1763286680&amp;width=500 500w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/Design_sans_titre_4.png?v=1763286680&amp;width=600 600w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/Design_sans_titre_4.png?v=1763286680&amp;width=800 800w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0956/0349/1142/files/Design_sans_titre_4.png?v=1763286680?v=1728926100&amp;width=1000 1000w\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"min(100vw, var(--page-width))\" style=\"\" class=\"\"></div>\n</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div></section>",
