        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "html": "<style>\n  .vasta-transform {\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n    background: #fff;\n    padding: 28px 0 22px;\n    width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-transform-header {\n    padding: 0 16px;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 18px;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-transform-title {\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #111;\n    line-height: 1.25;\n    margin: 0 0 8px;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-transform-title em {\n    font-style: italic;\n    text-decoration: underline;\n    text-decoration-thickness: 2px;\n    text-underline-offset: 4px;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-transform-subtitle {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #444;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    margin: 0;\n    font-style: italic;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-timeline {\n    position: relative;\n    padding: 4px 16px 0 46px;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-line {\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 26px;\n    top: 6px;\n    bottom: 10px;\n    width: 2px;\n    background: #111;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-step {\n    position: relative;\n    padding: 14px 0 10px;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-pill {\n    display: inline-block;\n    background: #FFD400;\n    color: #111;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    letter-spacing: .3px;\n    padding: 8px 12px;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    border: 2px solid #111;\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 0 #111;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-step-title {\n    margin: 0 0 6px;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #111;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-step-text {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    line-height: 1.65;\n    color: #1a1a1a;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-cta-wrap {\n    padding: 0 16px;\n    margin-top: 16px;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-cta {\n    display: block;\n    width: 100%;\n    text-align: center;\n    background: #FFD400;\n    color: #111;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    padding: 16px 14px;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    border: 3px solid #111;\n    box-shadow: 0 3px 0 #111;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  .vasta-cta:active {\n    transform: translateY(1px);\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 0 #111;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .vasta-transform-title { font-size: 21px; }\n    .vasta-step-title { font-size: 17px; }\n    .vasta-pill { font-size: 12px; padding: 7px 10px; }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"vasta-transform\">\n\n  <div class=\"vasta-transform-header\">\n    <h2 class=\"vasta-transform-title\">\n      Votre <em>Transformation</em> Semaine<br>après Semaine\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"vasta-transform-subtitle\">De la première goutte aux résultats durables</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"vasta-timeline\">\n    <div class=\"vasta-line\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n\n    <div class=\"vasta-step\">\n      <div class=\"vasta-dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n      <div class=\"vasta-pill\">JOURS 1-3</div>\n      <h3 class=\"vasta-step-title\">Le Démarrage En Douceur</h3>\n      <p class=\"vasta-step-text\">\n        Votre corps absorbe les ingrédients actifs et la détox s'enclenche. Une légère fatigue les premiers jours ?\n        C’est normal — votre corps élimine enfin.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"vasta-step\">\n      <div class=\"vasta-dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n      <div class=\"vasta-pill\">SEMAINE 1-2</div>\n      <h3 class=\"vasta-step-title\">La Détox S’Active</h3>\n      <p class=\"vasta-step-text\">\n        Foie libéré, parasites ciblés. Transit plus régulier et premiers signes d’énergie.\n        Votre corps sort du mode \"survie\".\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"vasta-step\">\n      <div class=\"vasta-dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n      <div class=\"vasta-pill\">SEMAINES 3-4</div>\n      <h3 class=\"vasta-step-title\">Les Premiers Vrais Changements</h3>\n      <p class=\"vasta-step-text\">\n        Ballonnements réduits, réveil facile, énergie stable toute la journée. Ventre plus plat, peau lumineuse.\n        Ça devient visible.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"vasta-step\">\n      <div class=\"vasta-dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n      <div class=\"vasta-pill\">1 MOIS ET +</div>\n      <h3 class=\"vasta-step-title\">La Transformation Durable</h3>\n      <p class=\"vasta-step-text\">\n        Résilience profonde installée. Foie optimal, intestin équilibré, énergie durable.\n        Les résultats s’installent — ils ne disparaissent pas.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"vasta-cta-wrap\">\n    <!-- Mets ton lien ici -->\n    <a class=\"vasta-cta\" href=\"/products/ton-produit\">JE COMMENCE MAINTENANT</a>\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
